      "content": "so r u saying that humanitarian stuff is basically just a distraction from real geopolitics? it feels like ur saying the only thing that actually matters is stability, and that even if you save thousands of lives, it's a \"failure\" if the politics gets messy later. is that the main way u view foreign policy, where human rights are secondary to power dynamics?",
